-- Auto Raposa Tavares to Issue 750 Million Reais in Debentures
-- B y   R a y m o n d   C o l i t t
-- 2012-11-15T20:05:19Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-11-15/auto-raposa-tavares-to-issue-750-million-reais-in-debentures.html
Brazilian road operator
Concessionaria Auto Raposa Tavares SA plans to issue non-
convertible debentures worth 750 million reais, according to a
regulatory filing.  The issue will take place on Dec.15, 2012, the Bauru-based
company said in a filing to the CVM today.  The offer is being coordinated by Banco Bradesco BBI SA,
Banco Votorantim SA, BB-Banco de Investimento SA, and HSBC
Corretora de Titulos e Valores Mobiliarios SA.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Raymond Colitt in Brasilia Newsroom at 
 rcolitt@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Joshua Goodman at 
 jgoodman19@bloomberg.net  